01:01:31.766 --> 01:01:35.110
The guys on your night shift
have to take the gloves off--

01:01:35.110 --> 01:01:37.250
so you always use euphemism--
take the gloves off.

01:01:37.250 --> 01:01:38.624
They have to break
the prisoners,

01:01:38.624 --> 01:01:41.780
so when we interrogate them,
they'll spill the beans.

01:01:41.780 --> 01:01:43.860
So essentially, you're
giving them total power.

01:01:43.860 --> 01:01:45.920
In three months,
there's no evidence

01:01:45.920 --> 01:01:49.030
that any senior officer ever
went down to the dungeon.

01:01:49.030 --> 01:01:51.420
So you're telling them, do
