01:01:57.430 --> 01:01:59.370
And on the day shift,
senior officers

01:01:59.370 --> 01:02:00.520
were there all the time.

01:02:00.520 --> 01:02:03.770
So essentially, the
message there is power

01:02:03.770 --> 01:02:06.690
without oversight, power
without surveillance

01:02:06.690 --> 01:02:09.360
is a recipe for abuse.

01:02:09.360 --> 01:02:11.730
