situation for that week.

01:02:18.680 --> 01:02:20.360
So that's a message.

01:02:20.360 --> 01:02:23.590
You give people absolute
power, and without oversight,

01:02:23.590 --> 01:02:26.460
without limits or without
constraints, over time,

01:02:26.460 --> 01:02:28.460
that power will be abused.

01:02:28.460 --> 01:02:31.640
And so my testimony reduced
