before the prisoner study

01:04:08.160 --> 01:04:10.510
based on "Lord of the Flies."

01:04:10.510 --> 01:04:13.730
So again, good literature
taps into good psychology,

01:04:13.730 --> 01:04:16.670
and what I try to do is
have good psychology map

01:04:16.670 --> 01:04:17.750
